OL,3,CDuke of Sussex meets Movember workers
OL,4,Con visit to men's health charity
OL,6,FThe Duke of Sussex greeted staff from
OL,7,FMovember as he paid a visit to the
OL,8,Fmen's health charity in Melbourne.
OL,10,FHarry met with members of the
OL,11,Forganisation on Wednesday morning at
OL,12,Fthe Whitten Oval, which is the
OL,13,Ftraining and administrative
OL,14,Fheadquarters of Australian rules
OL,15,Ffootball club Western Bulldogs.
