OL,3,CDuke of Sussex meets Movember workers
OL,4,Con visit to men's health charity
OL,6,FThe Movember movement, founded in
OL,7,FMelbourne in 2003, is a global charity
OL,8,Ffocused on improving men's health `
OL,9,Fparticularly in relation to mental
OL,10,Fhealth, suicide prevention, prostate
OL,11,Fcancer and testicular cancer.
OL,13,FThe campaign, which involves men
OL,14,Fgrowing moustaches during the month of
OL,15,FNovember to raise awareness, has
OL,16,Fraised hundreds of millions of pounds
OL,17,Facross more than 20 countries ` with
OL,18,F"Mo" commonly used in Australia as
OL,19,Fslang for moustache.
