OL,3,CDuke of Sussex meets Movember workers
OL,4,Con visit to men's health charity
OL,6,FSince its founding, Movember has
OL,7,Ffunded more than 1,250 men's health
OL,8,Fprojects around the world.
OL,10,FIt comes after the couple hugged
OL,11,Fpatients at a children's hospital as
OL,12,Fhundreds of people turned out to greet
OL,13,Fthem at the beginning of their visit
OL,14,Fto Australia on Tuesday.
OL,16,FHarry and Meghan spoke to children and
OL,17,Fposed for photographs with patients,
OL,18,Fas they were cheered by large crowds
OL,19,Fgathered along the walkways of the
OL,20,FRoyal Children's Hospital in Melbourne.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
