OL,3,CDuke of Sussex meets Movember workers
OL,4,Con visit to men's health charity
OL,6,FFollowing their visit to the hospital,
OL,7,FHarry and Meghan changed into matching
OL,8,Folive green outfits as they stopped at
OL,9,Fthe Australian National Veterans' Art
OL,10,FMuseum on Tuesday afternoon.
OL,12,FThe couple put on aprons and joined a
OL,13,Fpottery session with the children of
OL,14,Fveterans, known as "doves" by the
OL,15,Fmuseum, with Meghan crafting a clay
OL,16,Fostrich.
